            "id": 6124841,
            "title": "〈台股盤後〉「輝積」軍團暴衝 大漲512點收24277點再戰前高",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>在美國聯準會鮑爾釋出降息可能，及美國政府入股台積電疑慮消除下，台股今 (25) 日早盤開高走高，開 24108.81 點，上漲 344.34 點，隨即在台積電最高上漲 45 元，以及聯發科、鴻家軍，矽光子、機器人、軍工等主流族群全面走強下，指數最高上漲近 600 點。終場收 24277.38 點，上漲 512.91 點，一舉站上所有均線，並收復 24000 點大關，成交量 4178.33 億元。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6124841/l/28a80d729e0e91ef704419d633081340.jpg\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">〈台股盤後〉「輝積」軍團暴衝 大漲512點收24277點再戰前高。(圖：shutterstock)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>電子權值股紛紛勁揚，台積電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2330:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2330\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2330-TW</a>)(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:TSM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/TSM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">TSM-US</a>) 上漲 35 元，漲約 3%，收 1170 元；聯發科上漲 45 元，漲約 3%，來到 1415 元；日月光投控 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3711:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3711\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3711-TW</a>) 漲逾 3%，廣達 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2382:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2382\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2382-TW</a>)、鴻海 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2317:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2317\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2317-TW</a>) 漲逾 2%、聯電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2303:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2303\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2303-TW</a>) 均於平盤下方持平。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>輝達於官方社群帳號「X」預告將在 25 日晚間公開「機器人大腦」相關新品，帶動機器人類股走強，廣宇 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2328:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2328\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2328-TW</a>)、東元 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1504:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1504\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1504-TW</a>)、所羅門 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2359:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2359\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2359-TW</a>)、昆盈 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2365:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2365\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2365-TW</a>)、大銀微系統 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4576:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4576\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4576-TW</a>)、慧友 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5484:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5484\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5484-TW</a>)、新漢 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8234:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8234\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8234-TW</a>)、羅昇 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8374:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8374\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8374-TW</a>) 亮紅燈。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>輝達執行長黃仁勳 22 日來台，透露已向台積電送交矽光子處理器生產，激勵概念股走強，聯鈞 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3450:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3450\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3450-TW</a>)、光聖 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6442:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6442\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6442-TW</a>) 亮紅燈；上詮 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3363:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3363\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3363-TW</a>) 漲逾 7%，華星光 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4979:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4979\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4979-TW</a>)，波若威 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3163:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3163\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3163-TW</a>) 漲約 2%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>行政院明年度國防預算達史上最高 9495 億元，軍工族群再度噴出，雷虎 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8033:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8033\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8033-TW</a>)、中光電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5371:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5371\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5371-TW</a>)、佳世達 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2352:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2352\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2352-TW</a>) 攻上漲停板，漢翔 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2634:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2634\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2634-TW</a>)、長榮航太 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWG:2645:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2645\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2645-TW</a>) 漲逾 3%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
